						"subtitle": null,
						"subtitleSize": null,
						"copy": "The healthcare industry faces unique digital challenges — relentless data breach attempts, heavy reliance on third parties, and the need to deliver resilient virtual care despite constant attacks. Juggling all these challenges can take resources away from what truly matters: patient care. To reduce complexity, Cloudflare's connectivity cloud offers a unified platform to protect, connect, and accelerate digital healthcare operations\n\n- __Cost savings__: \nConsolidate critical security and connectivity services to improve agility and lower IT costs\n- __Better threat intelligence__: \nBlock more threats with Cloudflare intelligence gleaned from blocking ~227 billion threats daily\n- __Hybrid compatibility__: \nManage security and networking for complex environments (whether on-prem, hybrid cloud, or multicloud) from a single control plane",
